    "name": "Palm Beach Hotel & Resort",
    "detail": "I always try to stay close to airport when I depart Bali. Traffic can be a nightmare. Read the reviews of Palm Beach, all were good so I book 4 nights. I have found the perfect hotel which meets all my needs. Hotel is a short walk to beach, 10 minute walk to Lipton Mall and 15 minutes by taxi to airport. Hotel has well kept gardens, nice size pool and a elevated dining area overlooking pool. I booked a standard room, but having seen the deluxe room, it will be my next booking The best thing about this hotel it is so peaceful, you don't get the hawkers hanging around. Transport is easily arranged. Wonderful location.",
